::Dollen::

          Dollen looked at GoldenEye again.  This Predacon was actually
being nice to him, very unpredacon like.  Oh well, he needed a little help.

              "Hey, thanks," Dollen said, feeling surprised at himself.
Thanking someone was something he never did.  Something most Predacons never
do.  Another thought of the bot hit him.

             "Hey, umm, like I asked a minute ago, do you know of a female
bot with the beast mode of a silver fox??"
